      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i dont want to keep running back to the docs every week just for a tiny change like this. wouldn't it be pretty obvious if it was too low? like if i'm feeling healthy and my heart is fine, surely my body doesnt need the full 5mg anymore? it just seems like overkill if nothing is wrong.",
