      "content": "but u said it's individualized. if i've been stable on 5mg for a long time and i feel 100% fine, isn't the risk of a clot actually lower because my body has already adjusted? i just wanna know if there's a way to taper it myself safely so i dont have to deal with all the extra blood tests and doctor visits. like what would be a safe way to step down if i just wanted to try 2mg for a bit?",
